Package org.apache.drill.exec.expr

Class FilterBuilder

java.lang.Object
org.apache.drill.common.expression.visitors.AbstractExprVisitor<LogicalExpression,Set<LogicalExpression>,RuntimeException>
org.apache.drill.exec.expr.FilterBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
ExprVisitor<LogicalExpression,Set<LogicalExpression>,RuntimeException>
public class FilterBuilder extends AbstractExprVisitor<LogicalExpression,Set<LogicalExpression>,RuntimeException>
A visitor which visits a materialized logical expression, and build FilterPredicate If a visitXXX method returns null, that means the corresponding filter branch is not qualified for push down.
